---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Rumiano Cheese — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Founded in 1919 and the first West Coast plant to make organic cheese at scale, Rumiano is automating palletizing with Formic on a $0-upfront model to double packaging volume and invest in its community."
  ogTitle="Rumiano Cheese — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="106 years family-owned · doubling volume · zero upfront capital"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/rumiano-cheese" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Rumiano Cheese
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Rumiano Cheese</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Rumiano Automates with Formic to Drive Community, Culture, & Organic Cheese Dominance</h1>
    <p class="lede">Founded in 1919 and the first West Coast plant to make organic cheese at scale, Rumiano is automating palletizing with Formic — on a $0-upfront model — to double packaging volume and invest in a town of 6,000 people.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/rumiano-cheese-hero.jpg" alt="Rumiano Cheese packaging plant" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Rumiano Cheese · Willows, California</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1919</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Willows, California</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Family-owned cheese</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">In business</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">106 years</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Facility plan</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">50k → 200k sq ft</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Big growth, <em>small town</em>.</h2>
      <p>Rumiano Cheese, family-owned since 1919 (106 years), was the first West Coast plant to make organic cheese at scale, back in 2005. Its Willows, California packaging plant opened in 2021, and the company aims to double packaging volume by the end of 2026 and grow the 50,000-sq-ft facility to 200,000 sq ft over three to five years — all in a town of just 6,000 people.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Family-owned since 1919 — 106 years</li>
        <li>Organic cheese at scale since 2005</li>
        <li>Doubling packaging volume by end of 2026</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/rumiano-cheese-2.jpg" alt="Rumiano Cheese packaging operation" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Organic cheese · packaged</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">$0 upfront · RaaS</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Invest capital <em>where it matters most</em>.</h2>
      <p>After automating its labeling line and adding robotic arms on accumulators — moving employees into quality and slicing roles — Rumiano chose Formic in 2025 to automate palletizing on a $0-upfront Robotics-as-a-Service model, citing Formic's support and fast response without needing on-site robotics expertise.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Prior automation moved staff into quality roles</li>
        <li>Palletizing on a $0-upfront RaaS model</li>
        <li>Fast support — no on-site robotics expertise needed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"It was the level of support Formic provides. We don't have to have someone trained in advanced robotics on site, and knowing that Formic can come to our aid when we need it fairly quickly was what drove our decision."</blockquote>
      <cite>David Wolper · Director of Planning, Rumiano Cheese</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">It all comes back <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">to Rumiano's people.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">106</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Years family-owned</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">2x</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Packaging volume by 2026</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">4x</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Facility growth planned</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Build for <em>the next century</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
